dc_title_s: Shinkoku Kōso-shō zenzu; Nihon Sanbō Honbu.;淸國江蘇省全圖; 日本参謀本部.; 03 Kōso-shō zenzu;03 江蘇省全圖
dc_description_s: Relief shown by hachures. 04 Includes three insets: Nankin Kōneifujō no zu (scale 1:85,000); So-shūfujō no zu (scale 1:26,000); Shanhai ryakuzu (scale 1:50,000). 04 Includes three insets: 南京江寧府城之圖 (scale 1:85,000); 蘇州府城之圖 (scale 1:26,000); 上海略図 (scale 1:50,000). 1 map; 75 x 87 cm., folded in cover 23 x 17 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
